Well for starters, it's installed wrong. You put the "Cormorant Aeronology 1.5.1" folder in GameData. The contents of that folder are supposed to go into GameData, so it's "GameData/Cormorant Aeronology". That will make most of the parts fail to load because their models have paths like this: 

	model = Cormorant Aeronology/Assets/shuttleStack/CA_drogue

Fix that and try again. Here's the tutorial about installing mods if you'd like a refresher:
